title: The Best of Baking giveaway - Win baking prizes worth more than £3,700
text: We’ve teamed up with well-known household brands such as Joseph Joseph, Magimix and Kenwood to offer readers the chance to win one of many fantastic baking prizes. The prize draw is packed with all the baking essentials, from the latest kitchen technology with the Magimix Patissier multifunction, to five luxury Le Creuset baking sets. To enter, see the newspaper on Saturday, October 10. For an exclusive second chance to win, see the newspaper on Sunday, October 11. telegraph.co.uk Follow @telegraph
